# vhs script: render docs/doctor.gif showing mcx doctor output
Output docs/doctor.gif

Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1100
Set Height 380
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 18
Set TypingSpeed 22ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 0.85

Hide
Type "cd /Volumes/Projects/mincut-context"
Enter
Type "clear"
Enter
Show

Type "mcx doctor"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 4s
